Existing tablet users are requested to download our new application for tablets, AccuWeather, from here , https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.accuweather.android<p>Also a paid version of the application, AccuWeahter Platinum, is available:<br>https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.accuweather.paid.android</p><p>(These applications support notifications, severe weather alerts, landscape &amp; portrait and much more).</p><p>The most trusted weather information is now available through Google TV as well as on your Android tablet (for both Ice Cream Sandwich and Honeycomb operating systems). AccuWeather is an engaging, fully-featured, interactive weather application with an easy-to-use and playful interface. This truly is a one-of-a-kind application that will appeal to television viewers and tablet users alike. With GPS technology and interactive Google maps, the application makes it possible for you to get detailed and up-to-date weather forecasts and news on your television or tablet from the most trusted brand in weather.  <br> <br>Weather impacts everyone. From planning day-to-day activities to making future business or personal plans, you need fast, easy access to weather information from a reliable source. AccuWeather has all of the features and information that you need, is free of charge and will safeguard your daily and future plans from weather interruptions.</p><p>Weather Information:</p><p> Accurate and local forecasts for locations worldwide. Updated every hour, forecasts include the most detailed hourly forecasts for the next twenty-four hours, plus day and night weather forecasts and information for the next fifteen days  all available in 27 languages.</p><p> Current weather conditions are displayed with location name and time, temperature, humidity percentages, visibility, pressure, dew point, precipitation and amounts, UV index, and AM and PM times for sunrise and sunset.</p><p> The day and night weather forecasts for the next fifteen days also include, humidity percentages, precipitation and amounts, wind and wind gust speed, wind direction, and the exclusive, patented, RealFeel temperature  AccuWeathers proprietary weather forecasting system that takes into account multiple weather conditions to determine how the local temperature actually feels, which may be warmer or colder than the temperature depending on these conditions. </p><p> WeatherAlarms for locations worldwide, for weather events including, snow, ice, rain, wind, and thunderstorms. </p><p> Weather display options, including animated radar for North America, satellite and interactive Google maps for locations worldwide, and current, broadcast-quality weather videos.</p><p> Special lifestyle weather and health forecasts, as well as conditions for specific outdoor activities and sports, such as golfing, fishing, and jogging, and health-related weather forecasts, such as the hour-by-hour UV forecast, flu forecast, migraine headache forecast, and arthritis forecast. </p><p>Application Features: </p><p> Stores as many locations as the user chooses, with simple toggling between locations.</p><p> Navigation bar with easy-to-use buttons for toggling between each screen. Screens include Current, Hourly, Forecast, Maps, Lifestyle, News, and Settings. </p><p> The 24 hours of hourly data is available in a list format that scrolls when selected.</p><p> The user may choose between metric or English units, and either a 12-hour or 24-hour time display. </p><p> AccuWeather widgets are available for your home screens that link directly to AccuWeather. </p><p>Start accessing the most accurate and current weather information available through Google TV or your Android tablet. href="/store/apps/details?id=com.innocomm.clouddevice" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <h2> <a class="title" href="/store/apps/details?id=com.innocomm.clouddevice" title="Rooti CliMate"> 449.    Rooti CliMate  <span class="paragraph-end"></span> </a> </h2>   <div class="subtitle-container">  <a class="subtitle" href="/store/apps/developer?id=Rooti+Labs" title="Rooti Labs">Rooti Labs</a>   <span class="price-container"> <span class="paragraph-end"></span>   <span class="apps is-price-tag buy-button-container" data-doc-fetch-skip-cache="0" data-doc-fetch-vouchers="0" data-docid="com.innocomm.clouddevice"> <div class="pon" style="display:none">1</div> <button class="price buy id-track-click" data-server-cookie="CAIaIgogEh4KGGNvbS5pbm5vY29tbS5jbG91ZGRldmljZRABGAM=" data-uitype="223">    <span class="display-price"></span>   </button>    </span>     </span> </div>  <div class="description">  *** This app needs to work with Rooti CliMate *** <br>Rooti CliMate is a revolutionary app-cessory ( app+accessory) that accurately tracks the humidity, UV rays and temperature of your immediate environment, wherever you are. Its wireless, wearable, lightweight, tiny and very smart. It seamlessly syncs exact HUT information via Bluetooth back to our intuitive App on your iOS device every 15 minutes. It also tags the location and time of collection and under normal usage, a single coin cell battery lasts up to 6 months. So no recharging is necessary.<br>CliMate app is simple and beautiful. It syncs with the CliMate over Bluetooth and uploads the readings to a growing cloud database that visually and statistically show you your regions actual weather. The app is easy to set up, highly intuitive and interactive in a fun way. It continuously provides you with essential weather alerts and tips.<br>WHAT MAKES OUR APP GREAT?<br>1. Planted evidence. Weve designed our app so that it crunches all the most important data into a simple image that everyone will instinctively understand. A plant. This plant symbolizes you in relation to your surrounding climate. When youre protected, the plant flourishes. When youre exposed, it withers away. <br>2. Multiple-device hub. The app allows for multiple CliMates to be monitored. For example, you could keep a CliMate in the babys room, one in the vault or wine cabinet, and one on your bag. You can create your own label for each device and keep track of them simultaneously.<br>3. A history of HUT. The app parses all your data into daily, weekly and monthly charts with simple averages. This way you can gain visual insights into the long-term ramifications of your actual environment.<br>4. Red Alert. Based on your pre-entered information and the readings it receives, the app takes into consideration factors such as your skin tone and SPF sun cream in order to alert you to when its time to reapply actual sun protection. And avoid that red lobster look.<br>5. Pro-active Weather Tips and Warnings. Finally, the app analyzes all the user-generated cloud data and pro-actively warns you about harmful conditions. Forewarned is forearmed.<br>6. Share a snapshot of your local HUT. Choose a fun skin, take a picture and share with friends! <span class="paragraph-end"></span> <a class="card-click-target" href="/store/apps/details?id=com.innocomm.clouddevice" aria-hidden="true" Then,  sorry for these i can't respond. </p><p>IMPORTANT INFORMATION:<br>On the weather's Website that delivers the data currently, my account is in at Nov 27, 2013, since that the widget is published at the beginning of the month:<br>166.966 access, with 10.551 queries successful just for the day of Nov 26. (an average of about 8,000 the previous days)</p><p>Given the foregoing, it's very important that you use your own API key so that it continues to run, thank you.</p><p>It seems that, even with the new version, the Web server continues to update some data each day and don't returns any data in this case. On all of the new log of crashes i see are always "City appears to be empty". Be patient and try it again later. We work with the library developer to manage that, but it's not easy due the update of the server without any notice. thanks for understanding.<br>It's not the case for all version of Android and depends also of the phone's manufacturer.</p><p>Given the recent comments, if belching of some mutants such as no life could be described like that, I will stop my contribution on Google Play  for this widget for Italy.<br>These little shits will have to pay for apps instead of spitting on the work of others that they don't even pay. Coelho</a>   <span class="price-container"> <span class="paragraph-end"></span>   <span class="apps is-price-tag buy-button-container" data-doc-fetch-skip-cache="0" data-doc-fetch-vouchers="0" data-docid="com.productsofportugal.MeteoSats"> <div class="pon" style="display:none">1</div> <button class="price buy id-track-click" data-server-cookie="CAIaKgooEiYKIGNvbS5wcm9kdWN0c29mcG9ydHVnYWwuTWV0ZW9TYXRzEAEYAw==" data-uitype="223">    <span class="display-price"></span>   </button>    </span>     </span> </div>  <div class="description">  This app shows real-time meteorological satellite images, from available internet sources, covering virtually all regions of the world.<br>By looking at the animated meteo satellite images its easy to check the weather predictions very intuitively. <br>This app is complementary to other weather programs that don't have satellite images.<p>You can Zoom-in, Zoom-out, or move images around the screen just by sliding your fingers. <br>Rotate the device and the image will adapt to the screen automatically.<br>Share the images with your friends using other apps installed on your Android device (example: Facebook, Google+, WhatsApp, Viber, E-mail, etc). Enjoy!</p><p>Any suggestions you would like to see implemented in this app? Feel free to e-mail us with your comments. We are continuously trying to improve it.</p><p>Try also MeteoSatsPRO: </p><p>-Ads-free!<br>-Extra satellite pictures!<br>-North Pole and South Pole regions!<br>-Multilingual (English, Spanish, Portuguese, French, Italian, German...)</p><p><br>The images and data provided on by this app are provided as a public service and are not intended for operational or mission critical purposes. Weer Nu - Weerbericht Gratis  <span class="paragraph-end"></span> </a> </h2>   <div class="subtitle-container">  <a class="subtitle" href="/store/apps/developer?id=surfcheck.info" title="surfcheck.info">surfcheck.info</a>   <span class="price-container"> <span class="paragraph-end"></span>   <span class="apps is-price-tag buy-button-container" data-doc-fetch-skip-cache="0" data-doc-fetch-vouchers="0" data-docid="com.surfcheck.weathernow"> <div class="pon" style="display:none">1</div> <button class="price buy id-track-click" data-server-cookie="CAIaIgogEh4KGGNvbS5zdXJmY2hlY2sud2VhdGhlcm5vdxABGAM=" data-uitype="223">    <span class="display-price"></span>   </button>    </span>     </span> </div>  <div class="description">  De nieuwste weerapp van Nederland: supersnel, uitgebreid en vooral cht betrouwbaar. Met het live KNMI-weerbericht voor uw locatie.<p>Weer Nu biedt u:<br> De actuele weermetingen van uw locatie, rechtstreeks uit het KNMI-meetstationnetwerk.<br> Drie Radaranimaties, inclusief toekomstanimatie van Buienradar / Sneeuwradar en Europaradar.<br> Alle KNMI-live kaarten inclusief gevoelstemperatuur en Weeralarmkaart.</p><p>En ook:<br> Verwachtingen: per uur, twee dagen vooruit, de vijfdaagse verwachting en de tekstverwachting + KNMI verwachtingskaartjes.<br> Satellietbeelden: ieder uur ververst, uit drie verschillende bronnen.<br> De Pluimengrafieken met de vijftiendaagse temperatuur, wind en neerslagverwachting + sneeuwverwachting en ijspluim ( verwachte ijsaangroei ).<br> Bracknell, Hirlam en Sembachweerkaarten voor experts.</p><p>Widgets:<br> Het Weerstation met live weermetingen, werkt wereldwijd!<br> Live-icoon om het standaard-icoon te vervangen.<br> En de Zon en Maan-widget met op- en ondergangstijden, maanschijngestalten en -verlichtingsgraad.</p><p>Notificaties:<br> Toont u het weer op uw locatie in de notificatiebalk van uw androidtoestel!</p><p>Weer Nu is voorzien van een speciale tablet modus. En u kunt uw locatie zowel automatisch laten bepalen, als zelf instellen.<br> <br>(de widgets en notificatiefunctie zijn met een in-app betaling te activeren, dan verdwijnt ook de reclamebanner in de app).</p><p>Leveringsvoorwaarden:<br>We doen ons uiterste best om een fantastische en accurate weerapp te leveren, maar kunnen natuurlijk niet garanderen dat de software en de daarin gepresenteerde data altijd 100% correct werken en zijn. Daarbij kunnen databronnen soms wisselen en kunt u geen rechten ontlenen aan deze weerapp of de daarin gepresenteerde informatie. Door Weer Nu te downloaden en gebruiken accepteert u deze leveringsvoorwaarden.</p><p>Locatiegebruik<br>De locatiepermissie is alleen nodig voor de app en widgets om u de actuele weergegevens in uw omgeving te tonen. Deze locatiegegevens worden volstrekt anoniem verwerkt en door Surfcheck op geen enkele andere manier gebruikt.</p><p>Weer Nu is bedoeld als opvolger van onze weer app Het Weer in Nederland, en wil een van de meest complete weer apps van Nederland zijn. Deze app is alleen beschikbaar op Android 4 en hoger.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p> <span class="paragraph-end"></span> <a class="card-click-target" In fact, Notification Weather requires 0 clicks to operate as it runs entirely in the background, thus minimizing impact on battery life or data usage.</p><p>The forecast is placed directly in the notification dropdown and blends seamlessly with the operating system, leading you, the user, to believe it is part of the system. </p><p>Notification Weather is using Weather data from some of the best weather sources available including: Forecast.IO, Open Weather Map and  Yahoo! weather.</p><p>If you choose to upgrade to Premium you will also get:<br>- A refresh button and progress bar in notification that allows you to refresh the data manually<br>- Ability to open a different app when clicking on the notification<br>- 2 extra weather providers: AccuWeather and World Weather Online<br>- Option to get rid  the small notification icon in the status bar<br>- Option to Swipe the notification to dismiss, until next update.<br>- Ability to switch between 12/24 hour time format.</p><p><br>Support for other languages coming soon.   Hurricane - American Red Cross  <span class="paragraph-end"></span> </a> </h2>   <div class="subtitle-container">  <a class="subtitle" href="/store/apps/developer?id=American+Red+Cross" title="American Red Cross">American Red Cross</a>   <span class="price-container"> <span class="paragraph-end"></span>   <span class="apps is-price-tag buy-button-container" data-doc-fetch-skip-cache="0" data-doc-fetch-vouchers="0" data-docid="com.cube.arc.hfa"> <div class="pon" style="display:none">1</div> <button class="price buy id-track-click" data-server-cookie="CAIaGgoYEhYKEGNvbS5jdWJlLmFyYy5oZmEQARgD" data-uitype="223">    <span class="display-price"></span>   </button>    </span>     </span> </div>  <div class="description">  **One of the top 6 hurricane tracking apps - CNN**<br>**Readers Pick: Most innovative and useful hurricane app  FastCompany**<br>**One of 5 apps to get you through a natural disaster  Fox News**<br>**Top Apps of the Week (11/3/12)  ABC News**<br>**Top Apps of the Week (10/29/12) - MediaBistro**<br>**Top App of the week (9/2/12) - Appolicious**<p>Be ready for severe weather with Hurricane by American Red Cross. Monitor conditions in your area or throughout the storm track, prepare your family and home, find help and let others know you are safe even if the power is out  a must have for anyone who lives in an area where a hurricane may strike or has loved ones who do.</p><p>Ahora disponible en espaol.</p><p>Please note: shelters only show the current open shelters. More shelters are setup as disasters happen, but until then, there may not be any shelters near you.</p><p>Features:<br> - Easy to use Spanish language toggle to switch translation directly inside the app.<br> - Step-by-step instructions let you know what to do even if the cell towers are down and the power is out. <br> - Monitor weather conditions in your area or those of loved-ones with location-based alerts for the U.S. and its territories from the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration(NOAA).<br> - Let family and friends know you are okay with the customizable Im Safe alert for Facebook, Twitter, email and text. <br> - Find open Red Cross shelters in your area when you need help.<br> - Stay safe when the lights are out with the Hurricane Toolkit, including a strobe light, flashlight and audible alert functions. <br> - Prepare for the worst by learning how to assemble an emergency kit for your family in the event of power outage or evacuation.<br> - Empower your family to stay safe and remain calm in an emergency by learning how to make and practice an emergency plan. <br> - Earn badges that you can share with your friends and show off your hurricane knowledge with interactive quizzes.<br> - See an illustrated history of hurricanes in your area.<br> - Learn the difference between a hurricane warning and watch.<br> - Know how to what to do about food and drinking water when your area has been impacted by floods and power outages.</p><p>Please update your app to the latest version as soon as possible! It address numerous critical issues with crashing!</p><p>Permissions:<br>DIRECTLY CALL PHONE NUMBERS: We need this to allow you to call emergency numbers from within the app<br>CAMERA: We need to be able to use the camera to allow us to use the flashlight in Tool Kit<br>GPS LOCATION: We need to serve you hurricane alerts based on your current location<br>PHONE CONTACTS: We need this for the Make Wetter Online  <span class="paragraph-end"></span> </a> </h2>   <div class="subtitle-container">  <a class="subtitle" href="/store/apps/developer?id=WetterOnline+GmbH" title="WetterOnline GmbH">WetterOnline GmbH</a>   <span class="price-container"> <span class="paragraph-end"></span>   <span class="apps is-price-tag buy-button-container" data-doc-fetch-skip-cache="0" data-doc-fetch-vouchers="0" data-docid="de.wetteronline.wetterapp"> <div class="pon" style="display:none">1</div> <button class="price buy id-track-click" data-server-cookie="CAIaIwohEh8KGWRlLndldHRlcm9ubGluZS53ZXR0ZXJhcHAQARgD" data-uitype="223">    <span class="display-price"></span>   </button>    </span>     </span> </div>  <div class="description">  Ausgezeichnet als Testsieger mit der besten Wetterprognose (appgefahren.de, 02/2015)<p>Alles sofort sichtbar. Schnell, gut und kostenlos!</p><p> Das Wetter an Ihrem Standort<br> Vorhersage fr acht Tage<br> Im Stundentakt und fr Tagesabschnitte <br>  Regen: Wahrscheinlichkeit, Menge, Dauer<br>  Windstrke und Sonnenstunden<br> Wetterradar und Regenradar integriert<br>  Regenradar mit einstellbarem Loop<br>  Automatische Standortbestimmung<br>  Suchvorschlge<br> Weltweite Orte whlbar<br> Wetternews: Tglich die Top-Themen <br>  Wetterticker: Stndig das neuste zum Wetter<br>       Wintersport-Infos:  Schneehhen, Pistenzustand, Talabfahrten<br>       Wetterfoto: Umgebung fotografieren oder Wetterselfie machen und teilen</p><p>Das Wetter an Ihrem Ort wird inklusive Wettervorhersage, Regenradar oder Wetterradar sofort angezeigt. Wechseln Sie durch Wischgesten zwischen dem Regenradar und dem Wetterradar fr den ausgewhlten Ort. ber die Wettervorschau fr die nchsten drei Stunden und Tage erfahren Sie sofort, ob es Regen geben wird oder ob die Sonne scheint.</p><p>Wischen Sie den unteren Bereich nach links, so erhalten Sie die Wetterbersicht fr die kommenden Stunden und Tage.</p><p>Jeden beliebigen Ort weltweit knnen Sie ber die komfortable Suchfunktion problemlos finden, zu Ihren Favoriten hinzufgen und dann direkt aufrufen.</p><p>Tippen Sie auf das Regen- oder Wetterradar, so wird es bildschirmfllend angezeigt. Starten Sie den Loop und sehen Sie, wohin der Regen in den nchsten 90 Minuten ziehen wird. Natrlich knnen Sie auch Einzelbilder anschauen und so noch genauer erfahren, wo es regnen wird.</p><p>Das Wetterradar zeigt Ihnen, wo gerade die Sonne scheint und wo Wolken den Himmel bedecken. Natrlich knnen Sie auch erkennen, wo Regen, Schnee oder Hagel fllt und wo gerade Blitze und Gewitter auftreten. Temperaturwerte runden das umfangreiche Informationsangebot ab.</p><p>ber das integrierte Men sind weitere Inhalte wie zum Beispiel Ihre Favoriten oder der Wetterticker mit nur einem Klick erreichbar.</p><p>Der Wetterticker von WetterOnline bietet umfassende Informationen zum Wetter  direkt aus der WetterOnline-Redaktion. An sieben Tagen pro Woche wird mit hoher Aktualisierungsfrequenz ber das Wetter berichtet. Bei brisanten Wetterlagen berichten unsere Meteorologen rund um die Uhr und bercksichtigen Wettermeldungen von Nutzern via Twitter und Facebook. Aktuelle Videos knnen unmittelbar angesehen und alle Inhalte schnell und einfach in die sozialen Netzwerke geteilt werden. Und wer mchte, kann einzelne Beitrge im Wetterticker direkt kommentieren und mit anderen Nutzern ber das Wetter diskutieren.</p><p>Im Menpunkt Wetternews finden Sie u.a. unsere Top-Themen, den Wetterbericht fr Deutschland, das 14-Tage-Wetter und das Wochenendwetter. Unsere Meteorologen analysieren fr Sie alle Berechnungen der Wettermodelle und fassen diese fr Sie einfach und verstndlich zusammen.</p><p>Die WetterApp bietet Widgets, mit denen man das Wetter sofort im Blick hat. Um die Widgets zu nutzen, muss die App aufgrund von Vorgaben des Android-Betriebssystems im Telefonspeicher installiert werden. </p><p>Das 2x1-Widget zeigt das aktuelle Wetter. Die 4x1- und 4x2-Widgets bieten aktuelles Wetter und Vorhersagen. Alle Widgets sind fr den Standort und fr jeden anderen Ort whlbar. Bei allen Widgets sind Farbe und Transparenz einstellbar.</p><p>Sie mchten die WetterApp werbefrei nutzen? Dann installieren Sie unsere App Wetter Pro.</p><p>Alle Informationen der App knnen Sie direkt in Ihre sozialen Netze teilen. This network of Davis stations is fed by thousands of businesses, schools, and hobbyists who have chosen to share their data with the world.  Adding your own station is easy, and requires only a permanent Internet connection, a nice place to put your outdoor sensors, and a few hundred dollars burning a hole in your pocket.</p><p>The interface was designed to take advantage of the Android platform, and includes many standard features found in your favorite apps.  In addition to the WeatherLink Network, WeatherLink Mobile also reports data from all NOAA and National Weather Service feeds.</p><p>2012 Davis Instruments Corp.</p><p></p><p></p> <span With the Met Office app you can get these UK and worldwide forecasts wherever you go. You can also subscribe to push notifications in the Met Office app, alerting you of any UK National Severe Weather Warnings issued. <p>Key features: </p><p> Free to download <br> 5- day forecasts for over 5,000 UK locations <br> Push notifications for UK National Severe Weather Warnings for your chosen regions <br> Text and maps detailing UK National Severe Weather Warnings <br> Hourly UK location forecasts for first two days <br> Three-hourly UK forecasts for days 3-5 <br> Three-hourly daily forecasts for numerous international locations <br> Save up to 10 favourite UK or international locations <br> Regularly updated with the latest forecast and warning information <br> Social media sharing so you can share forecasts with friends and family </p><p> Includes  <br>- UV forecast maps <br>- Probability of precipitation <br>- Temperature and Feels like temperature <br>- Sunrise and sunset <br>- Visibility <br>- Wind speed and direction </p><p>Please note the map layers will work best over 3G or WiFi. </p><p>This popular app won Best App 2012 at the Sparkies 2013 Awards, has achieved AQuA (App Quality Alliance) standard and has been nominated for a number of industry awards. </p><p>This app does not support landscape view, and whilst it may work on some tablets it has not been built to support tablet use. </p><p>This app is ad-supported. We do not provide refunds under any other circumstances. Unlike regular programs they don't just install themselves in the application tray so you have to add them manually. They will not open or launch.<br>Here's how to add a widget on your Android home screen.</p><p>STEPS HOW TO ADD A WIDGET<br>==========================<br>1.On your Android home screen, tap any blank or empty area with size 4x2 and hold down your finger.<br>2.An Add to Home screen window will pop up. From that window, tap Widgets.<br>3.Youll be presented with a list of all the installed Widgets on your Android device.<br>4.Select the clock to add to your home screen by tapping it.</p><p>Notes<br>=====<br>"Time frozen/not updating"-&gt; taskiller killed the clock(exclude it from taskillers)<br>When phone starts, clock starts in less than a min too.</p><p>ROM users-&gt; make sure the clock is NOT moved on SD card.<br>Widgets are not supposed to be on SD card. Move it back to the phone storage.</p><p>Weather hint: For world destinations with two words in the name, type in the box the words with a plus sign.<br>For example "Buenos Aires" type "Buenos+Aires",remember the "+" sign -no spaces, don't include the quotes.</p><p>Email problems/suggestions<br>Check our website for more help.</p><p>EXCLUDE IT FROM TASKILLERS!!!<br>Be polite, this "Buenos+Aires",remember the "+" sign -no spaces, don't include the quotes.</p><p>Email problems/suggestions<br>Check our website for more help.</p><p>EXCLUDE IT FROM TASKILLERS!!!<br>Be polite, this is a free app :-)</p><p>VIDEO HOW TO ADD WIDGETS<br>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DpMLF9b2aTQ</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p> <span Weather Delta  <span class="paragraph-end"></span> </a> </h2>   <div class="subtitle-container">  <a class="subtitle" href="/store/apps/developer?id=Felker+Tech" title="Felker Tech">Felker Tech</a>   <span class="price-container"> <span class="paragraph-end"></span>   <span class="apps is-price-tag buy-button-container" data-doc-fetch-skip-cache="0" data-doc-fetch-vouchers="0" data-docid="com.felkertech.n.weatherdelta"> <div class="pon" style="display:none">1</div> <button class="price buy id-track-click" data-server-cookie="CAIaJwolEiMKHWNvbS5mZWxrZXJ0ZWNoLm4ud2VhdGhlcmRlbHRhEAEYAw==" data-uitype="223">    <span class="display-price"></span>   </button>    </span>     </span> </div>  <div class="description">  There are some great weather apps out there. They are pretty accurate, tell you the weather for days and weeks, and give you a lot of different numbers.<p>Here's the problem with that: what do numbers mean? Have you ever looked outside and said, "Oh, the barometer is going to be 29.3 in/HG today." Even if you knew that number, how would you conceptualize it?</p><p>Weather Delta gives users a good idea of how weather changes. Okay, so the temperature is 60 degrees now. Over the course of the day though, the temperature will drop. It's really easy to see changes and each metric has a summary of the data. This makes it much easier to plan your day because you can conceptualize the change based on current conditions instead of absolute conditions.</p><p>Powered by Forecast.io, Weather Delta is also really easy to set up. You open the app, and you get the local weather. It couldn't be much easier.</p><p>It will notify you throughout the day if there's any significant change in the weather. </p><p>The app also supports Android Wear. When paired to a mobile device, a wearable will get a series of cards which provide users with a beautiful weather station on their person.</p><p>It's the first weather app to support Android TV. It can still pull your location and display the weather in a way that's optimized for a television.</p><p>FEATURES<br>- Supports Lollipop<br>- Android Wear support, with beautiful notifications<br>- Android TV support, download it from the web<br>- Change between English units and metric<br>- Grabs current local weather and analyzes change<br>- Notifies users of weather changes<br>- It's all about the user. You can change your comfort levels for wind, temperature, and more so that you only get notified of important things.</p><p>PREMIUM<br>An in-app purchase gives users additional features and helps support development<br>- Full offline app for Android Wear<br>- View the current weather with the "Delta Face" watchface</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p> <span
